    <item>
      <title>亚利桑那州参议院投票废除 1864 年以来的州堕胎禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/arizona-senate-secures-enough-votes-to-repeal-1864-abortion-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚利桑那州参议院以 16 比 14 的投票结果废除了 1864 年一项将几乎所有堕胎定为犯罪的法律，在该州最高法院于 4 月初恢复了内战时期的法律后，保留了堕胎程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/arizona-senate-secures-enough-votes-to-repeal-1864-abortion-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩特罗表示哥伦比亚将与以色列断绝外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/president-petro-says-colombia-to-cut-diplomatic-ties-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗在周三的劳动节假期演讲中表示，哥伦比亚将与以色列断绝外交关系，因为以色列有“一位种族灭绝的总统”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/president-petro-says-colombia-to-cut-diplomatic-ties-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:03:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因支持俄罗斯战争而制裁中国和阿联酋的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-sanctions-firms-in-china-uae-for-support-of-russia-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周三宣布对包括中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国在内的近 300 家公司和个人实施制裁，理由是它们涉嫌支持俄罗斯入侵乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-sanctions-firms-in-china-uae-for-support-of-russia-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和沙特签署近邻防御协议旨在重塑中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-and-saudis-near-defense-pact-aimed-at-reshaping-middle-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国和沙特阿拉伯即将达成一项历史性协议，该协议将为沙特提供安全保障，并为以色列政府结束加沙地带战争奠定与以色列建立外交关系的可能途径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-and-saudis-near-defense-pact-aimed-at-reshaping-middle-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:42:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国监管机构讨论最早于八月敲定银行资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些批评人士呼吁放弃这一具有里程碑意义的计划，美联储和其他美国顶级监管机构仍在继续推进该计划，让大银行持有更多资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约警察局在大学校园镇压中逮捕了 300 多名抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ny-police-amass-near-columbia-as-adams-tells-protesters-to-leave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对以色列与哈马斯战争的愤怒，纽约警察驱散了两所大学不断升级的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动，逮捕了近 300 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ny-police-amass-near-columbia-as-adams-tells-protesters-to-leave</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 01:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院通过俄罗斯铀进口禁令，送交拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/senate-passes-russian-uranium-import-ban-sending-bill-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院周二晚间投票通过了禁止从俄罗斯进口浓缩铀的法案，并将该法案提交总统审议。据白宫称，拜登总统计划很快将该法案签署成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/senate-passes-russian-uranium-import-ban-sending-bill-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 23:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
